Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
The portfolio is located in Olean, NY along the main business corridor and is approximately 1 mile to Olean General Hospital and 2.5 miles to Saint Bonaventure University. 

Olean is a city in Cattaraugus County and serves as its financial, business, transportation and entertainment center. It is one of the principal cities of the Southern Tier region of Upstate New York.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE|Buffalo has been retained as the exclusive advisor in the sale of a four (4) building medical complex in Olean, New York. The four (4) buildings total ±28,139 SF and are situated on seven (7) tax parcels and comprise ±2.4 acres. The property is currently 100% leased to three (3) tenants.

Interested parties are asked to sign a confidentiality agreement to gain access to the offering memorandum.
